eu.digitisation.Page

Class Sort

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.digitisation.Page.Sort

  • public class Sort
extends Object
    PAGE-XML regions order in the document can differ form reading order. Such information is stored under OrdereGroup (recursive) elements. This class restores the appropriate order of elements in the document.
    Author:
    R.C.C.
